node.text:
Watch to see how we capture Henry + Baloo’s special moments and learn some tips + tricks you can use to photograph your amazing pets! 

#ad Thanks to our friends @samsungmobile we filmed everything with our #GalaxyS21 Ultra for the new Master It creator classes, and wow ... it is incredible. Seriously can’t wait to share some more photos/videos with you and show you how to #MasterIt #withGalaxy

node.text:
Henry and Baloo mean the WORLD to us, so it’s a bit scary when we travel if either of them were to get sick. Which is why we started using @vetster.inc! Now we can reach licensed and verified veterinarians from anywhere, 24/7, and get Henry + Baloo the care they need right away ❤️

Download the Vetster app and get 50% off your first appointment by using our code HENRYBALOO50 , link in bio!
#ad #GetVetster #AnytimeAnywherePetCare

node.text:
HAPPY 7th BIRTHDAY Henry!!!🎉 
Can’t wait to take you on so many more adventures because we know that’s what you really want for your birthday. But don’t worry you’ll be getting cake and presents tonight too because you deserve all of it, sweet boy 🧡 Happy Birthday Bubba, we love you so stinking much.

node.text:
Sleep under the stars with us tonight for @eddiebauer’s annual event ✨ Pitch a tent in the backcountry or in your own backyard so we can all watch the stars together, no matter where you are ❤️ We’re so excited to sleep under the stars with you all tonight!! 
#SleepUndertheStars #FindYourselfOutside #ebcontributor

node.text:
To infinity and beyond! ✨ 

Henry got to try out this packable dog backpack from @petsmart and is loving it. It’s lightweight, has just the right amount of storage for a day hike, is reflective, and packs right into itself for easy carry! To snag one for your pup’s adventures, click the link in our bio. 
#AnythingforPets #ArcadiaTrail #sponsored
